profile:
Inspection Proof. Inc. is a company which deals with infrared home and property inspections. They also work in real estate dealings. They perform the infrared thermal scan of your home or property.

A qualified inspector of the Inspection Proof Inc utilizes Infrared Thermal Imaging to analyze surface temperature variations specific to moisture, electrical, structural and heating problems. 

A qualified inspector of the Inspection Proof Inc reviews the homes Structural System, Exterior, Roof System, Plumbing System, Electrical System, Heating System, and Air Conditioning Systems as well.
